data.description: NORTH CLEVELAND | REMODELED SINGLE LEVEL HOME - This charming single level home is completely remodeled and ready for you to move in! As you enter the home, you'll notice the new flooring and fresh paint throughout. The spacious living room provides ample space for everyone and leads you into the kitchen with painted cabinets and stainless appliances. Entertaining and gathering can be held in the oversized dining room with a stunning fireplace as the focal point. Off the dining room, a sunroom provides an ideal spot for enjoying your morning coffee or favorite book. The primary bedroom is a true retreat with an en suite bathroom featuring a walk-in shower. Two more bedrooms provide you with additional privacy and comfort and share a full bathroom with a subway tile shower. The large, level backyard includes a detached shed that is great for all of your storage needs. Located in North Cleveland just moments from the Greenway and downtown, you don't want to miss out on this beautiful home!
